{"tid":844044,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"肥媽咁撚毒既 推人買商用公寓","createTime":"2018-10-01T14:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:06:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"867110ac0ff7a39b18282eebd1e8859f82b2d73a","tid":844044,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355137bb00ebcab4cb8b743d8666197d30e6283d","tid":844044,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abdb7bad0f313fe583db343aee44066744da4cd","tid":844044,"uid":123456,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話<br />\n南亞狗冇一個係無辜</span></span>"},{"pid":"913ec00d2940e2b7961b428b0db304a362e4f7c2","tid":844044,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老味50萬中山新樓"},{"pid":"6ea57190947f70a473d9958cebec0996f3d62867","tid":844044,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"忠實粱粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e78bfe60d2760bafd3ee635b84f72fc839b911","tid":844044,"uid":80724,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"一見到佢講大灣區三個字就想星佢一大把"},{"pid":"8464501ac016e3d322661c75e6ce3354d05677ec","tid":844044,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"馬子妮好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd3288bbc5f8dcc2590993ed998b864343b74f9","tid":844044,"uid":213762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d62f12a9ff10d295bd148b6c609e519d535b3c","tid":844044,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"公寓爆发！在中山投资商业公寓是馅饼还是深坑？<br />\n<br />\n根據專業人士介紹，商業公寓在轉手的時候，要繳納四種稅費，其中契稅3%、個稅（能提供不動產發票，則按照差額的20%，如果沒有則全額的1%）、土地增值稅（如果提供不動產發票則按照差額的30%&mdash;60%，如果麽沒有則全額8%）、增值稅及附加差額5.6%，主城區和郊區的稅率可能會略有不同。<br />\n按照這個公式，給大家簡單算一個賬：<span style=\"color: red;\">50萬買入一套公寓，2年後評估價為80萬元，此時轉手意味著，你要繳納各種稅費約20.38萬</span>（按照評估的市場價格為準計算，且所有稅點按照最低計算）<br />\n震驚嗎？相當於50%以上的利潤，沒了！<br />\n公寓變現能力很差，實在不太好賺差價。所以買公寓一定要做好長期持有的心理準備，長期持有出租，收取租金，相當於在銀行存了一個定期，可以作為一種&ldquo;整存零取&rdquo;的理財方式。<br />\n<br />\n首付高，產權年限低<br />\n商業公寓首付5成，年限最多只能按10年，商業利率1.1倍；一般不能使用公積金貸款，產權年限一般只有40年。<br />\n<br />\n商水商電，居住舒適度差<br />\n公寓房的水電費都是按商業用電的標準繳納，所以購買和居住公寓的成本都比較高。公寓房一般都是不通天然氣的，炒菜只能用電磁爐之類，且廚房一般為開放式，容易有油煙味；戶型通透性一般，居住舒適度較低。公寓房子戶型一般都很小。大概50-70平米。整體結構不平整，視覺上有壓迫感。<br />\n<br />\n市場需求和流動性遠不如住宅<br />\n住宅自帶剛性需求，漲幅一般較快，遇到市場好的時候，可能價格一兩年翻一番。投資住宅實現收益的方式主要靠轉手賺取差價。而投資商用公寓則是長線投資，需要放長線釣大魚，通過城市利好、區域利好、城市更新利好以及產品自身優勢一步步的釋放公寓價值，釋放周期較長。<br />\n如果你了解了以上購買公寓的優缺點，還是決定要投資公寓， 這裏，提供一個公寓購買攻略！"},{"pid":"4ed85513bac3d892dcac00449bb890bd37d6e55f","tid":844044,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"355137bb00ebcab4cb8b743d8666197d30e6283d","tid":844044,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9011b073dbcaf6c9092e47910283352056ca0c9","tid":844044,"uid":72045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0abdb7bad0f313fe583db343aee44066744da4cd","tid":844044,"uid":123456,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話<br />\n南亞狗冇一個係無辜</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"肥媽葡人黎..."},{"pid":"cca5d5c4f4819134785fb33c6a89db2dc769399b","tid":844044,"uid":53206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"仲有政策因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700780acf42312bb515bf64709621fc1c0f90685","tid":844044,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"911b4b1391d1f8c37934c48665b0e334ba89d691","tid":844044,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T22:52:50.000Z","msg":"肥閪只不過係一個見錢開眼嘅肥婆<br />\n有錢搵<br />\n叫佢畀佢個閪你屌埋都仲得"},{"pid":"7982ebbeeddc8738e26748c15eff807a2227fab1","tid":844044,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"仲話用黎自住on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投資還投資 自住還自住<br />\n變左大閘蟹就自住安慰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d10158e82f6ae500b187276419265de3c6505b9","tid":844044,"uid":32282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8464501ac016e3d322661c75e6ce3354d05677ec","tid":844044,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"馬子妮好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"6adb8bde65254dd8c6122994da5bb9825d0f4f63","tid":844044,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da13bea488f818cb04b83a6a08a5c625128245f","tid":844044,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911b4b1391d1f8c37934c48665b0e334ba89d691","tid":844044,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T22:52:50.0